metadata.description:
It's a reusable widget that can be used for creating rooms for chats, games and so on. Feel free to fork and contribute!

Props:
```{
  "widgetKey": "yourwidgetkey",
  "widgetName": "Your widget title",
  "loadRoomCallback": "<your callback>",
  "initialValue": {...}
}```

**widgetKey**: All the data is stored in users' accounts. So all the data will be under the key that you mention in this property. 
**loadRoomCallback**: A function. It will be called when the room will be loaded
